title: AMAZING X-MEN 001 (2013) (Marvel) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)
description:
Story by Jason Aaron
Art by Ed McGuinness, Dexter Vines
Colors by Marte Gracia
Letters by VC - Joe Caramagna
Covers by Ed McGuinness, Marte Gracia, Milo Manara, more...

Publisher: Marvel Comics
Cover Price: $3.99
Release Date: November 6th, 2013

An AMAZING new era for the X-Men starts here!

Ever since Nightcrawler's death in X-MEN: MESSIAH COMPLEX, the X-Men have been without their heart and soul. After learning that their friend may not be gone after all, it's up to WOLVERINE, STORM, BEAST, ICEMAN, NORTHSTAR and FIRESTAR to find and bring back the fan favorite fuzzy blue elf!

Superstar artist ED MCGUINNESS (HULK) joins master X-Writer JASON AARON (WOLVERINE AND THE X-MEN) to bring you the most exciting comic on the stands!
